# Navigation v1.4.5 — Quick Reference

Source: `docs/Navigation_v1.4.5_consolidated.md`

## Screen Registry: Buyer (24) + Picker (5) = 29 screens
- Auth: AuthPhoneScreen, AuthOTPScreen
- Catalog: HomeScreen, StoreScreen, ProductListScreen, ProductDetailScreen
- Search: SearchScreen, SearchResultsScreen
- Cart/Payment: CartScreen, PaymentMethodScreen, OrderConfirmationScreen, PaymentWebView, SBPPaymentSheet
- Orders: OrderTrackingScreen (3 tabs), OrderDetailScreen, OrderHistoryScreen
- Profile: ProfileScreen, PaymentMethodsScreen, AddressScreen, AddressEditScreen, SettingsScreen
- Alerts: SmartAlertsScreen, AlertDetailScreen
- Favorites: FavoritesScreen
- Picker: PickerOrderListScreen, PickerOrderDetailScreen, PickerScanScreen, PickerHistoryScreen, PickerProfileScreen

## Tab Bar
- Buyer: Home | Search | Cart | Favorites | Profile (5 tabs)
- Picker: Orders | History | Profile (3 tabs)

## Deep Links (6 routes)
`robinfood://store/:id`, `robinfood://order/:id`, `robinfood://product/:id`,
`robinfood://order/:id?tab=chat`, `robinfood://orders`, `robinfood://order/:id?action=arrived`

## A11y (WCAG 2.1/2.2 AA)
- Touch targets ≥ 44×44pt, contrast ≥ 4.5:1, all elements have accessibilityLabel + Hint
- Amounts in a11y: use formatPrice() per Spec sec 14.3

